Privacy Policy

Introduction

Thank you for using our EMI calculator. We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This privacy policy explains how we handle your personal information when you use our EMI calculator.

What Information Do We Collect?

We do not collect any personal information from you when you use our EMI calculator. We do not store or retain any data from your calculations.

How Do We Use Your Information?

We do not use your information for any purpose. We do not share your information with any third parties.

Do We Disclose Your Information?

We do not disclose your information to any third parties.

